sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant AuthProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod
    participant Workers as Ray Workers
    participant ServeSvc as Serve Service<br/>8000/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation & Dashboard Access (OpenShift/RHOAI)

        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (RayCluster created)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Worker Pods,<br/>Services, RBAC<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>CertMgr: Create Issuer + Certificates<br/>(mTLS for head/workers)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute, ReferenceGrant,<br/>Auth proxy sidecar, NetworkPolicy

        Note over Gateway,Dashboard: External user accesses Ray Dashboard
        User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}/<br/>Session cookie
        Gateway->>AuthProxy: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed TLS)
        AuthProxy->>AuthProxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get service/{cluster}-head-svc)
        AuthProxy->>Dashboard: Proxy to localhost<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (loopback)
        Dashboard-->>AuthProxy: Dashboard HTML
        AuthProxy-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: Dashboard UI
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Operator,Workers: Flow 2: RayJob Submission (HTTPMode)

        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (RayJob created)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ephemeral RayCluster<br/>(if submissionMode: HTTPMode)
        Operator->>Dashboard: POST /api/jobs/<br/>Submit job payload<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (cluster-internal)
        Dashboard->>HeadPod: Schedule Ray tasks
        HeadPod->>Workers: Distribute work<br/>gRPC, mTLS (if enabled)
        Workers-->>HeadPod: Task results
        Operator->>Dashboard: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>Poll job status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
        Dashboard-->>Operator: Job status (SUCCEEDED/FAILED)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob status
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Operator,ServeSvc: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Upgrade

        User->>K8sAPI: Update RayService CR<br/>(new serveConfigV2)
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (RayService updated)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create pending RayCluster
        Operator->>Dashboard: PUT /api/serve/applications/<br/>Push Serve config to pending cluster<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
        Dashboard-->>Operator: Config applied

        loop Health Check Loop
            Operator->>ServeSvc: GET health check<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
            ServeSvc-->>Operator: Application health status
        end

        Note over Operator: All apps healthy on pending cluster
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Switch Service selector<br/>active ↔ pending<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Note over ServeSvc: Traffic atomically switches<br/>to new cluster
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Delete old RayCluster
    end
